	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories Pretoria - An aircraft had to make an emergency landing next
to the N1 highway near Hammanskraal, north of Pretoria, on Monday morning,
Tshwane emergency services said. "It was basically an emergency landing next to the
freeway close to Hammanskraal, but nobody was injured," spokesperson Johan
Pieterse said. The plane had two occupants.   24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.